OL,3,CPolice force apologises to family of
OL,4,Cman who died after train crash
OL,6,FSpeaking to the PA news agency, the
OL,7,Ffamily friend said: "The fact is that
OL,8,Fon the night in question, she (Rachel
OL,9,FEvans, Mr Evans' wife) was pretty much
OL,10,Fleft to her own devices, support
OL,11,Fwasn't adequately provided at the
OL,12,Ftime."
OL,14,FOn October 22 the force put out a
OL,15,Fstatement saying, "the deceased's next
OL,16,Fof kin have been informed and his
OL,17,Ffamily are being supported by
OL,18,Fspecialist officers".
OL,20,FBut a specialist officer from the BTP
OL,21,Fvisited the family only on October 23.
