OL,6,FThe friend also said the family also
OL,7,Fobjected to media reports suggesting
OL,8,Fthe cause of death.
OL,10,F"Currently, news outlets are putting
OL,11,Fout that the cause of death was not
OL,12,Frelated to the collision without any
OL,13,Fevidence," he said.
OL,15,F"The opening of the inquest was
OL,16,Fyesterday, and the cause of death is
OL,17,Fstill indeterminate."
OL,19,FBTP superintendent Andrew Morgan
OL,20,Fapologised for their earlier statement.
