OL,3,CPolice force apologises to family of
OL,4,Cman who died after train crash
OL,6,FHe said: "We would like to apologise
OL,7,Ffor a miscommunication issued shortly
OL,8,Fafter the train collision which took
OL,9,Fplace on Monday October 21 in
OL,10,FLlanbrynmair.
OL,12,F"British Transport Police has
OL,13,Fapologised directly to the family of
OL,14,Fthe deceased in relation to this
OL,15,Fstatement and would like to apologise
OL,16,Fpublicly for any additional suffering
OL,17,Fcaused at this extremely difficult
OL,18,Ftime."
