OL,3,CPolice force apologises to family of
OL,4,Cman who died after train crash
OL,6,FLouisa Corcoran, assistant coroner for
OL,7,FCeredigion, opened an inquest into his
OL,8,Fdeath at the Aberystwyth Justice
OL,9,FCentre on Wednesday, 30 October.
OL,11,FShe said a post-mortem examination is
OL,12,Fin progress and adjourned the inquest
OL,13,Fwhile the police investigation was
OL,14,Fongoing.
OL,16,FFour other people suffered serious
OL,17,Finjuries during the incident, and a
OL,18,Ffurther 11 sustained injuries
OL,19,Frequiring hospital treatment.
