OL,3,CPolice force apologises to family of
OL,4,Cman who died after train crash
OL,6,FInvestigators from the Rail Accident
OL,7,FInvestigation Branch (RAIB) suspected
OL,8,Fthe incident was caused by slippery
OL,9,Frails.
OL,11,FThe RAIB has said the condition of the
OL,12,Ftrack on the approach to the collision
OL,13,Fpoint meant "adhesion" between wheels
OL,14,Fand rails was "relatively low".
OL,16,FIt said this suggested an Aberystwyth-
OL,17,Fbound train may have slid while
OL,18,Fbraking, causing it to crash at a
OL,19,Fspeed of around 15mph into a
OL,20,Fstationary train destined for
OL,21,FShrewsbury.
